Real Women Have Curves;;75;;85;;PG-13;;Curves on a blossoming young woman can be sexy, but not if you are told you have too many of them. "Real Women Have Curves" is a humorous and warmhearted look at a Mexican-American teenage girl coming of age in a boiling cauldron of cultural expectations, class constrictions, family duty, and her own personal aspirations.;;Drama,Comedy;;Patricia Cardoso;;2002;;America Ferrera,Lupe Ontiveros,Ingrid Oliu,George Lopez,Brian Sites,Jorge Cervera Jr.,Felipe de Alba,Soledad St. Hilaire,Lourdes Perez,Jose Gerardo Zamora Jr.,Manuel Edgar Lujan;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/real_women_have_curves